doc.title: Kakaretso ea Link Open With extension
doc.description:
Katoloso ena e o thusa ho laola ka tsela e bonolo hore na lihokelo li buloa joang.

Fensetere: libatli tse ling, lifensetere tse pop-up, lifenstere tse ncha, lifenstere tse ncha tsa incognito, fensetere ea hajoale (ea kamehla)

Li-tabs: ka ho le letšehali ho ea hajoale, tab ea hajoale, ka ho le letona ho ea hajoale (ea kamehla)

Maemo a ho kenya tšebetsong: ha a sebetse, kenya tšebetsong hang-hang (ka ho sa feleng)
